sentence: Moving over to the US, the release of the 7/31 Federal Open Market Committee (FOMC) minutes this Wednesday will be the key catalyst.
Note that US homebuilders have been down in the last few weeks, and as a result, investors are watching to see if demand has softened following pressure from rate increases.

Specifically, earnings releases to keep an eye on include Home Depot ( HD ), and housing data indicators include existing home sales for July on Wednesday, home prices on Thursday, and new home sales on Friday.
Separately, retail earnings hit this week and will give analysts some more color on consumer sentiment (note - disappointments in Walmart - WMT and Nordstrom - JWN last week).
Specialty retailer Urban Outfitters ( URBN ) will report after the close today.
